# limit-merge

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `limit_sort_optimization_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (limit ?n1 ?off1 (limit ?n2 ?off2 ?input))
rhs: (limit ?n1 ?off1 ?input)
